<p>#1: No, I don't think you can leave off the first quoted url in Textile.<br />
#2: No you'd definitely would need to modify Textile for this. Or, even better: Parse incomplete url's like in your example *before* you run the Textile parser over it. If you need to know how to do this, check out this paste:</br></p>
